      "text": "調子がいいみたいだな。一体何を意識したら\nあそこまでいい表情が出来るようになるんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It seems like you're in great spirits.\nWhat exactly are you focusing on to achieve such great expressions?",
        "id": ""
