    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_03-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "最初に練習した時は、予め考えた表情とポーズを\n出来るだけ正確に決めるってことばかり考えてたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I started practicing‚ I used to focus solely on nailing\nthe predetermined expressions and poses as accurately as possible.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_03-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "それこそ雫ちゃんの言う魂が入りようのない\n形だけのポーズ……って感じでしたよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It felt like I was just going through the motions‚\nwith no real soul in my poses‚ as Shizuku-chan put it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
