      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_03-ngs015.m4a",
      "text": "仕事を受ける時は不安でしたけど……\n自分の新しい可能性を見つけられて良かったです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was nervous when I took on this job…\nBut I'm glad I discovered new possibilities for myself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 140.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_03-ngs016.m4a",
      "text": "これからは新たな売りとして\n小悪魔伊吹渚を推してもいいですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "From now on‚ can I promote myself\nas the Little Devil Nagisa?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 145.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、それもアリだけど、意図的に推すなら\nそれこそ、こころくらいやりきらないとダメだと思うぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ that's an option‚ but if you're going to intentionally promote that persona‚\nYou'll need to commit to it as much as Kokoro does.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 153.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_03-ngs017.m4a",
      "text": "う、それは険しい道のりですね……\n確かに、こころちゃんは徹底してますもんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ that's a challenging path…\nCertainly‚ Kokoro-chan is very thorough.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 162.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、こころもあの振る舞いが性に合ってるから\nずっと続けられるんだと思うけどな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ Kokoro sticks with that behavior because it suits her personality.\nI think she can keep it up for a long time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "でも、渚の新しい武器であることは間違いないから\nたまに見せる分にはいいと思うぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But there's no doubt that it's a new weapon for you‚ Nagisa.\nI think it's fine to show it from time to time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 174.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
