      "text": "{user}さんの手……あったかいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san's hand… it's warm.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 216.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_03-ngs024.m4a",
      "text": "この楽屋ちょっと寒かったから、ちょうどいいですね\nえへへ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This dressing room was a little cold‚ so it's just right.\nEhehe.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 224.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_03-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "おい、何を……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ what are you…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 227.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_03-ngs025.m4a",
      "text": "ん～？　どうしましたか～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm? What's the matter~?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 229.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_03-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "こ、こら！　渚！\nもう小悪魔の練習は終わっただろう！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey! Nagisa!\nDidn't you finish practicing being a little devil already?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_03-ngs026.m4a",
      "text": "いやいや\nこころちゃんに比べたらまだまだですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh no‚ not yet.\nI still have a long way to go compared to Kokoro-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 239.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_03-ngs027.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんも\nさっきそう言ってましたもんね……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ {user}-san also said earlier…\n\"Occasional practice is essential‚\" right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 243.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_03-ngs028.m4a",
      "text": "それに、たまに見せればいいからってサボってたら\n絶対うまくいかないですもん。隙あらば修行、ですよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And if I slack off just because you said I should show it from time to time‚\nIt won't work out at all. Practice whenever there's an opening!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 249.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_03-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それはそうだけど、そういうことじゃなくて……\nもう、勘弁してくれ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ that's true‚ but I didn't mean…\nCome on‚ cut me some slack…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 259.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
